Huge Price Adjustment & SOLAR PANELS INCLUDED!!  Additional incentives include - Seller contributions of $10,0000.00 towards Buyers closing cost.
 8103 Prescott Dr- Located in the desirable Heritage Oaks. Open concept floor plan invites sunshine to flow room- to -room. Experience the allure of this 4 bedrooms /3 FULL bath + a spacious flex room. As you step inside you will be captivated by the extend entry effortlessly leading you to the gourmet kitchen. Designed to delight any chef, boast beautiful custom white cabinetry, stainless appliances & designer backslash. Wood looking tile flooring graciously flows throughout the entire home offering durability for your daily activities. Unwind in the primary bathroom offering separate vanity sinks, generous walk-in shower, pampering soaker tub & huge primary closet. All secondary bedrooms are spacious offering ceiling fans ,2-inch blinds & sizable closets. Additional amenities include, NO CARPET , SOLAR PANELS, full irrigation, outdoor kitchen set up with refrigerator & MUCH more. Don't miss the opportunity to own this "like new" beauty. Call TODAY!
